summary: My first Dungeon mod please endorse if you like.
descriptionHtml:
New huge hardcore dungeon full of interesting secrets, traps, treasures, secret ways and other interesting things. It\'s NOT a boring dungeon with clear corridors, rooms and boring traps with thousands of monsters. This dungeons is about secret places, hidden treasures, unusual traps and other cool things. It will be hard to find all secrets and avoid all traps in this dungeon. Some parts of this dungeon are under water. So of course for argonians it will be a bit easier to explore everything.
No Requirements
The Dungeon is near riverwood.
Cave Name is Unknown Cave,
author: FusionDent
